== 用途 ==
=== 古代 ===
研究發現[[舊石器時代|舊石器時代]]至[[中石器時代|中石器時代]]初期，樺焦油就被廣泛作為[[粘合劑|粘合劑]]使用；已知[[尼安德塔人|尼安德塔人]]早於20萬年前就通過乾餾[[白樺|白樺]]樹皮的方式生產樺焦油<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Kozowyk|first=P. R. B.|last2=Soressi|first2=M.|last3=Pomstra|first3=D.|last4=Langejans|first4=G. H. J.|date=2017-08-31|title=Experimental methods for the Palaeolithic dry distillation of birch bark: implications for the origin and development of Neandertal adhesive technology|journal=Scientific Reports|language=En|volume=7|issue=1|pages=8033|doi=10.1038/s41598-017-08106-7|pmid=28860591|pmc=5579016|issn=2045-2322}}</ref>。從2019年開始的一項研究表明，樺木焦油的生產可能是一個非常簡單的過程，僅需在露天條件下並利用光滑的垂直表面來收集燃燒樺樹皮所產生之[[焦油|焦油]]<ref>{{Cite journal|author=Schmidt, P.|author2=Blessing, M.|author3=Rageot, M.|author4=Iovita, R.|author5=Pfleging, J.|author6=Nickel, K. G.|author7=Righetti, L.|author8=Tennie, C.|title=Birch tar extraction does not prove Neanderthal behavioral complexity|journal=PNAS|doi=10.1073/pnas.1911137116|pmid=31427508|volume=116|issue=36|pmc=6731756|year=2019|pages=17707–17711}}</ref>。為在[[荷蘭|荷蘭]][[北海_(大西洋)|北海]]的罕見證據表明，尼安德塔人使用樺焦油製作小型“家用”石製工具<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Niekus|first=Marcel J. L. Th.|last2=Kozowyk|first2=Paul R. B.|last3=Langejans|first3=Geeske H. J.|last4=Ngan-Tillard|first4=Dominique|last5=van Keulen|first5=Henk|last6=van der Plicht|first6=Johannes|last7=Cohen|first7=Kim M.|last8=van Wingerden|first8=Willy|last9=van Os|first9=Bertil|last10=Smit|first10=Bjørn I.|last11=Amkreutz|first11=Luc W. S. W.|date=2019-10-21|title=Middle Paleolithic complex technology and a Neandertal tar-backed tool from the Dutch North Sea|url=https://www.pnas.org/content/early/2019/10/15/1907828116.short?rss=1|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|volume=116|issue=44|language=en|pages=22081–22087|doi=10.1073/pnas.1907828116|pmid=31636186|pmc=6825292|issn=0027-8424}}</ref>。
[[中石器時代|中石器時代]]遺跡中更發現有利用樺焦油將{{le|箭翎|Fletching}}及[[箭鏃|箭鏃]]接合於[[弓箭|弓箭]]上與利用樺焦油固定綑綁用的{{le|生皮|Rawhide (material)}}圈來製作[[斧|石斧]]等證據。

[[芬蘭|芬蘭]]{{le|基里基|Kierikki}}發現了距今有5000年的樺焦油製[[口香糖|口香糖]]，且至今仍帶有牙齒印記<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/6954562.stm|title=Student dig unearths ancient gum, 2007.|access-date=2021-02-01|archive-date=2017-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170913000219/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/6954562.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。保留在口香糖中的遺留物質使人們得以進行有關人口流動、食物類型以及牙齒上細菌的類型等研究<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/2019/12/17/science/ancient-gum-dna.html Ancient gum DNA] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/12/17/science/ancient-gum-dna.html |date=20210205180809 }}'', Science, The New York Times, December 17, 2019</ref>。[[丹麥|丹麥]]南部亦發現了距今有5700年的樺焦油製口香糖；研究團隊從咀嚼的樺焦油中檢測出完整的[[人類基因組|人類基因組]]和口腔微生物組。研究人員發現咀嚼者為女性，與[[歐洲大陸|歐洲大陸]]的[[狩獵採集者|狩獵採集者]]在遺傳上有密切相關性<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Jensen|first=Theis Z. T.|last2=Niemann|first2=Jonas|last3=Iversen|first3=Katrine Højholt|last4=Fotakis|first4=Anna K.|last5=Gopalakrishnan|first5=Shyam|last6=Vågene|first6=Åshild J.|last7=Pedersen|first7=Mikkel Winther|last8=Sinding|first8=Mikkel-Holger S.|last9=Ellegaard|first9=Martin R.|last10=Allentoft|first10=Morten E.|last11=Lanigan|first11=Liam T.|date=2019-12-17|title=A 5700 year-old human genome and oral microbiome from chewed birch pitch|journal=Nature Communications|language=en|volume=10|issue=1|pages=1–10|doi=10.1038/s41467-019-13549-9|pmid=31848342|issn=2041-1723|pmc=6917805}}</ref>。
