=== 現代 ===
{{le|俄羅斯皮革|Russia leather}}由於[[鞣製|鞣製]]後增加塗抹樺焦油的程序來達到防水效果，並且樺焦油供應的地理限制，使其成為17世紀和18世紀[[俄羅斯帝國|俄羅斯帝國]]的主要出口商品<ref name="HCC, Juchten" >{{Cite web
| title=Production of Russia Leather
| year=1807
| url=http://www.thehcc.org/Juchten.pdf
| publisher=The Honourable Cordwainers' Company
| access-date=2013-10-04
| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304030315/http://www.thehcc.org/Juchten.pdf
| archive-date=2016-03-04
}}</ref>。塗抹樺焦油不只阻止了[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]的侵襲，並且增加怡人香氣的散發，被視為[[皮革|皮革]]品質的指標。樺焦油也用作[[香水|香水]]的基礎調香，賦予香水[[皮革|皮革]]、[[焦油|焦油]]、[[煙熏|煙熏]]和[[冬青|冬青]]的香氣；{{le|帝國皮革|Imperial Leather}}和某些肥皂亦將樺焦油作為增添香氣的成分。

樺焦油為一種有效的[[腹足綱|腹足綱]]{{le|動物驅逐劑|Animal repellent|驅逐劑}}<ref name="Lindqvist 2010">{{cite journal | last1 = Lindqvist | first1 = I. | last2 = Lindqvist | first2 = B. | last3 = Tiilikkala | first3 = K. | last4 = Hagner | first4 = M. | last5 = Penttinen | first5 = O.-P. | last6 = Pasanen | first6 = T. | last7 = Setälä | first7 = H. | year = 2010 | title = Birch tar oil is an effective mollusc repellent: field and laboratory experiments using ''Arianta arbustorum'' (Gastropoda: Helicidae) and ''Arion lusitanicus'' (Gastropoda: Arionidae) | journal = [[Agricultural_and_Food_Science|Agricultural and Food Science]] | volume = 19 | issue = 1| pages = 1–12 | doi = 10.2137/145960610791015050 | doi-access = free }}</ref> ，驅逐劑效果可持續約兩週<ref name="Lindqvist 2010"/>。樺焦油與[[凡士林|凡士林]]混合塗抹後柵欄對腹足綱的驅避力可持續數月之久<ref name="Lindqvist 2010"/>。並且由於大量的[[酚類|酚類]]衍生物和[[萜烯|萜類]]衍生物，使得樺焦油具有很強的[[防腐|防腐]]能力<ref>Wanamaker, L, [https://otzispouch.ca/birch-tar-oil-a-powerful-antiseptic/ "Birch Tar Oil A Powerful Antiseptic"] {{Wayback|url=https://otzispouch.ca/birch-tar-oil-a-powerful-antiseptic/ |date=20201209203644 }}, ''OtzisPouch'', 2020-04-01</ref>。

=== 藥用 ===
[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]將樺焦油用於製作治療[[皮膚|皮膚]][[創傷|創傷]]、[[燒傷|燒傷]]、[[潰瘍|潰瘍]]和[[化膿|化膿]]的{{le|維斯涅夫斯基擦劑|Vishnevsky liniment}}<ref name="bmj">{{cite journal |title=Vishnevsky liniment and ichthammol: on the perspectives of application in military medicine and other fields |journal=[[英國醫學期刊|英國醫學期刊]]|volume=318 |issue=7198 |pages=1600–1604 |doi=10.1136/bmj.318.7198.1600|pmid=10364122 |pmc=1115970 | date=12 June 1999|last1=Charman |first1=C. }}</ref>；然而長期使用將增加[[皮膚|皮膚]]和造血系統生長[[惡性腫瘤|惡性腫瘤]]的風險。<ref>Sergei V. Jargin. Vishnevsky liniment and ichthammol: on the perspectives of application in military medicine and other fields (komentarz to artykułu Atopic eczema). „BMJ”. 318 (1600), 2014. [[DOI|DOI]]: [https://www.bmj.com/content/318/7198/1600 10.1136/bmj.318.7198.1600] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bmj.com/content/318/7198/1600 |date=20210205150304 }} (ang.).</ref><ref name="bmj"/>

樺焦油常用於製作治療[[皮癬菌病|皮癬菌病]]及[[單純疱疹病毒|單純疱疹病毒]]的各式[[處方藥|處方藥]]，如軟膏、糊劑，溶液的濃度範圍為1-30％<ref name=Rozanski>Henryk Różański. [http://luskiewnik.strefa.pl/pix/p10.htm Dziegieć brzozowy.] {{Wayback|url=http://luskiewnik.strefa.pl/pix/p10.htm |date=20170520020603 }} W: Dziegcie i smoły pochodzenia roślinnego i mineralnego – Pices (Pyrolea)</ref>。

[[波蘭|波蘭]]將樺焦油限制為需[[處方|處方簽]]要求之{{le|調配藥|Compounding}}<ref>Wojciech Chmielak: [https://receptura.pl/ Ściąga z receptury] {{Wayback|url=https://receptura.pl/ |date=20210125132029 }}. Szczecin: www.receptura.farmacja.pl, 2011, s. 23.</ref><ref> [http://dziennikmz.mz.gov.pl/legalact/2016/39/ Obwieszczenie Prezesa Urzędu Rejestracji Produktów Leczniczych, Wyrobów Medycznych i Produktów Biobójczych z dnia 6 kwietnia 2016 r. w sprawie ogłoszenia Urzędowego Wykazu Produktów Leczniczych Dopuszczonych do Obrotu na terytorium Rzeczypospolitej Polskiej.] Dziennik Urzędowy Ministra Zdrowia, 2016-04-06. [dostęp 2016-11-24].</ref>；[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]和[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]則為管制寬鬆之[[成藥|成藥]]。
